list.abstract: 《TESTING》是吴亦凡于2020年4月22日发行的专辑，其中收录了四首歌曲，其中三首中文歌由吴亦凡一首包办词曲创作及制作。

yingyinNormal.en: Testing the limits of the human spirit.
yingyinNormal.zh: 测试人的精神极限。

yingyinNormal.en: He's spent months timing testing his monkey face design.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他花数月时间计时和测试猴脸设计。

yingyinNormal.en: Mr. Joshua, I would not describe your product testing as perfected.
yingyinNormal.zh: 约书亚先生，测试的结果并不如人意。

yingyinNormal.en: Well you don't. Yes I do! Good! Good! I was just testing you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你是不爱他了。我爱。很好，我只是在测试你。

yingyinNormal.en: The rocket they are testing is believed to be big enough to reach the West Coast of the United States.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们的测试火箭，规模大到可以抵达美国西岸地区。

yingyinNormal.en: Is this testing whether I'm a Replicant or a lesbian, Mr. Deckard? Just answer the questions, please.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是在测试我是不是女同复制人么，狄卡先生？请直接回答问题。

yingyinNormal.en: Take this to the testing area, put your name at the top, sign the bottom, answer the questions, bring it back. Next!
yingyinNormal.zh: 带这个去测试区，在上面写上名字，下面签字，回答完问题交回来，下一个！

yingyinNormal.en: A friend at the School of Pharmacology gave me these new pills they're testing. He says it's the next big thing for social anxiety disorder.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我在药学院的一个朋友给了我这些他们正在测试的药，他说这将是治疗社交焦虑障碍领域的又一奇迹。

yingyinNormal.en: We are testing a new medication for social anxiety, panic attacks, agoraphobia and obsessive compulsive disorder. Why would they be looking for test subjects here?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们正在测试一种新药，专治社交焦虑症恐慌发作症，陌生环境恐怖症和强迫症，他们为什么要在这招人？

yingyinNormal.en: I've got to go. I've got to get up early. My company's testing a new steroid that supposedly doesn't shrink testicles, and the last one there has to do the measuring.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我得走了，明天我还得早起，我们公司在测试一种据说不会让睾丸缩水的新类固醇，最晚上班的人要负责测量睾丸的工作。

yingyinNormal.en: Attention, all initiates report for final testing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 请注意，所有新成员，来最终测验报道。

yingyinNormal.en: After testing Mr. Keller's fields, what did you find?
yingyinNormal.zh: 检测过凯勒先生的土地后，你发现了什么？

yingyinNormal.en: What happens next? Oh, more testing, more success, more fame.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那接下来怎么办？更多的实验，更多的成功，当然，还有更多的荣誉。

yingyinNormal.en: I want you to start testing the revised 112 on chimps ASAP.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我要你尽快在黑猩猩上试验改进后的112号药。ASAP=as soon as possible
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Rise of the Planet of the Apes》

yingyinNormal.en: Mr Carson, they've been testing the system since the Romans left.
yingyinNormal.zh: 卡森先生，自从罗马人离开，社会就一直在经受考验。

yingyinNormal.en: Mother Nature's way of testing her creations. Refining the pecking order.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是大自然母亲检测她产物的方式，调整食物链。

yingyinNormal.en: To our friends in the west, whose idea of war is a remote testing location.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我亲爱的西方朋友，你们以为战争只存在于遥远的荒漠。

yingyinNormal.en: Anyway, great catching up. Now, who's ready to move on to live penguin testing?
yingyinNormal.zh: 无论如何，来得太及时了。现在，谁准备好进行活企鹅实验了呢？

yingyinNormal.en: Leonard's new girlfriend is testing Bernadette's loyalty to you and the group. That bitch is crafty.
yingyinNormal.zh: 莱纳德的新女友在检验伯纳黛特对你和咱们的忠心呢，那个贱人真狡猾啊。

yingyinNormal.en: Testing it. Seeing how it handles. I could take you, if you like. Would you? Well, I'd like to see it. How about you? I'll be in London on Wednesday.
yingyinNormal.zh: 试驾，看看车况如何，你愿意的话我可以送你去。是吗？我也想看看，你呢？周三我要去伦敦。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2015-2022年全国卷高考试卷，包括阅读、完形、单选、填空、听力、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。
